videos.headline: Herbert drops dime to Mitchell for TD
videos.description: Oregon's Justin Herbert throws a perfect pass to wide receiver Dillon Mitchell for the 34-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Oregon comes up with key blocked punt
videos.description: Oregon's Kano Dillon comes through the line and blocks the punt giving Oregon great field position.

videos.headline: Utah QB gives them the lead late in 4th
videos.description: Utah quarterback Jason Shelley runs it in from 2 yards out giving Utah the lead late in the fourth quarter.
